"My husband and I know exactly what we want - steak frites, mine au poivre, and his natural, with a Caesar salad.  Perfectly cooked and delicious, every time.  The staff at Mon Ami Gabi is professional and friendly.  We were warmly welcomed and treated really well.  Thank you for a wonderful evening!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "AlbertR", "datePublished": "2023-11-08T18:15:00-05:00", "reviewBody": "Great overall experience.! From menu options and quality of food to excellent service.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 4, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 4}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Lauren", "datePublished": "2023-11-05T11:00:00-05:00", "reviewBody": "The crepes were outstanding! We will return again and again.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "RKLewis", "datePublished": "2023-11-01T18:30:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Food quality has significantly declined over the past few years.  Steak frites was uninspiring - steak was mediocre and the fries were soggy.  The restaurant is really showing wear and tear and feeling rundown.  Service was fine.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 2, "bestRating": 3, "worstRating": 2}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Leijla", "datePublished": "2023-10-31T19:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "What I was most impressed with about Mon Ami Gabi was the service. Everybody who waited on us or interacted with us was friendly and helpful. The atmosphere was great. I wish they had more vegan-friendly options on the menu (that's my one criticism).", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 4, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 4}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "OpenTable Diner", "datePublished": "2023-10-28T20:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Dinner was delicious and came out perfectly timed. We loved our cocktails too! Husband got the Bee Sting and I got the Whiskey Ginger. Enjoyed the atmosphere and will definitely be going back for another date night with the hubby:)", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 4}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "PageH", "datePublished": "2023-10-27T17:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "The food was delicious as always. I tried to use my points to pay for the meal and the server charged me and my friend instead. I asked him to correct it and we waited for a long time and eventually gave up. Very disappointed in the server.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 3, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 1}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "RestonRestReviews2023", "datePublished": "2023-10-27T12:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Service was at best amateurish .  From timing of the different courses to the poor communication , the service was poor.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 2, "bestRating": 3, "worstRating": 1}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "evpearl", "datePublished": "2023-10-22T18:45:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "The food was great. The ladies\u2019 room was a mess. I spoke to our server about it, but all that had been done an hour later was the addition of a roll of toilet paper \u2014 and it was simply placed on top of the dispenser. Our server needed remedial training. And it wasn\u2019t just our table that was having issues with her. The other servers we watched were doing a good job, describing dishes, engaging guests and checking on them regularly. We experienced none of that. Needless to say, my boyfriend\u2019s birthday dinner experience wasn\u2019t what I hoped it would be.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 3, "bestRating": 4, "worstRating": 1}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "WiliamN", "datePublished": "2023-10-21T18:15:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Mon Ami Gabi is always consistent in the quality of its French cuisine and the service is outstanding. Yesterday\u2019s dinner was no exception.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "RayB", "datePublished": "2023-10-18T17:30:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Delicious food and a delightful wine and spirits selection paired with an inviting ambiance. Loved it!!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 4, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 4}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Reina", "datePublished": "2023-10-15T11:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Brunch here was amazing! Our server was excellent and even obliged our group by taking many photos of us. Sorry we broke the water bottle!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Flora8353", "datePublished": "2023-10-14T18:15:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Great food, service and ambiance!\nAppetizers are great!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 4, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 4}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "W003", "datePublished": "2023-10-13T18:45:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Food was delicious and service was excellent. However, we were seated in an addition that was separated by a curtain to what I think it is a kitchen prep section which was noisy.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 2}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Stev", "datePublished": "2023-10-13T17:45:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "The food was tasty. Portions were large. Service was less than acceptable. For example desert was served but we had to call two different waiters to get silverware. Similarly coffee came without silverware or sweetener which we requested in advance. The bill had a 3% charge for food price increases that was \"optional\" but we had to ask to have it removed. If Mon Ami Gabi want to increase prices 3%, it should change its menu. This is one of the restaurants that fought against a 3% meals tax a few years ago claiming it would hurt its business and now it's imposing it's own tax in a hidden manner. If you eat here tell them you don't want to pay the surcharge!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 2, "bestRating": 3, "worstRating": 1}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Lynn", "datePublished": "2023-10-11T18:45:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "We had a wonderful evening at the restaurant, and were provided outstanding service by Herman.  We enjoyed oysters, trout, and the week\u2019s special of beef Wellington. That, along with a good bottle of wine, the night was wonderful.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "MarkM", "datePublished": "2023-10-10T18:45:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Great classic steak frites.  Bit noisy on the night I went, but service was top notch.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 4, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 3}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "OpenTable Diner", "datePublished": "2023-10-08T15:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Service was slow, inattentive lacks dining skills. Steak tartare was brown in color indicating lack of quality and freshness.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 2, "bestRating": 3, "worstRating": 2}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "IleanaR", "datePublished": "2023-10-07T19:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Last nights meal was wonderful. We enjoyed a nice table (in a corner, not next to other guests), our server was very attentive and professional. Our meal was fantastic, we both ordered the 3 mini filets with bordelaise sauce &amp; frites. The Caesar salad was great, and the chocolate souffl\u00e9 dessert was delicious!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "MSB52", "datePublished": "2023-10-07T18:15:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "All my favorite French bistro food with ambiance and good service. Escargot, French onion soup, steak frittes, decent 