al price. Important Info Please note that direct views of the track from our patio and glass pavilion seating areas are not guaranteed. Monitors with race weekend coverage will be on display throughout the restaurant from Thursday, November 16 \u2013 Saturday, November 18. Guests will be given lanyards for their specific package upon entry, and a confirmation email prior to the weekend to assist at security checkpoints. All packages are non-refundable. Please email\u00a0 MonAmiVegasParties@lettuce.com \u00a0to inquire about special bookings and customizable options. Choose your package on Tock  or  reserve on Thursday and Friday  to join us at Mon Ami Gabi to soak in the most extravagant experience of the year on the Las Vegas Strip! *This promotion is not in correlation with tickets sold for the 2023 Las Vegas Grand Prix. Stay in Touch Sign up for our email list to stay up to date on exclusive offers, special events, seasonal specials, and more. Join Our Receive texts for for special offers and updates! Standard message and data rates of  your carrier may apply, you can expect recurring messages monthly from an automated system and can text STOP to cancel or HELP for help at any time. Consent to text messaging terms not required for purchase. Must be 21 years or older to participate.  Mobile Terms and Conditions  &  Privacy Policy 3655 S Las Vegas Blvd Las Vegas, NV  Sunday \u2013 Thursday\u00a0\u00a07:00 AM \u2013 10:00 PM Friday \u2013 Saturday\u00a0\u00a07:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM Breakfast\u00a0\u00a07:00 AM \u2013 11:00 AM Lunch\u00a0\u00a011:00 AM \u2013 4:00 PM Dinner\u00a0\u00a04:00 PM \u2013 Close  LETTUCE.COM FREQUENT DINERS GIFT CARDS ACCESSIBILITY EMPLOYMENT PRIVACY POLICY TERMS OF USE \u00a92023 Mon Ami Gabi\u00ae. A Lettuce Entertain You\u00ae Restaurant. We use cookies to provide the best experience on our website. By continuing to use our site you agree to  our updated privacy policy . Start the festivities on Thursday, November 16 or Friday, November 