inner was no exception.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "RayB", "datePublished": "2023-10-18T17:30:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Delicious food and a delightful wine and spirits selection paired with an inviting ambiance. Loved it!!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 4, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 4}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Reina", "datePublished": "2023-10-15T11:00:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Brunch here was amazing! Our server was excellent and even obliged our group by taking many photos of us. Sorry we broke the water bottle!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 5}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Flora8353", "datePublished": "2023-10-14T18:15:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Great food, service and ambiance!\nAppetizers are great!", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 4, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 4}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "W003", "datePublished": "2023-10-13T18:45:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "Food was delicious and service was excellent. However, we were seated in an addition that was separated by a curtain to what I think it is a kitchen prep section which was noisy.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": 5, "bestRating": 5, "worstRating": 2}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": "Stev", "datePublished": "2023-10-13T17:45:00-04:00", "reviewBody": "The food was tasty. Portions were large. Service was less than acceptable. For example desert was served but we had to call two different waiters to get silverware. Similarly coffee came without silverware or sweetener which we requested in advance. The bill had a 3% charge for food price increases that was \"optional\" but we had to ask to have it removed. If Mon Ami Gabi want to increase prices 3%, it should change its menu. This is one of the restaurants that fought against a 3% meals tax a few years ago claiming it would 